Interface Movable

All Known Implementing Classes:
Bullet, CandidateIcePeashooter, CandidatePeashooter, CrazyZombie, ExplodingHead, IcePeashooter, LevelInstruction, Peashooter, Sprite, Sun, Zombie
public interface Movable
The Movable interface represents any object in the game that can move, be drawn, detect collisions, and expire.
